# Box Shadow

CSS box-shadow generator

## Online Tool

Use this tool online at **[DevTools.at](https://devtools.at/tools/box-shadow)** - Free, fast, and no registration required!

## Installation

```bash
pip install devtools_box_shadow
```

## Usage

```python
from devtools_box_shadow import process, encode, decode

# Process input
result = process("your input here")

# Encode
encoded = encode("data to encode")

# Decode
decoded = decode("data to decode")
```

